thread.title_full: Reid Cycles reviewed by Nick Williams

author: Nick Williams
title: Nick Williams
text:
On a Sunday evening I ordered a vintage bella for my partner's birthday, which was on Tuesday. I had no expectation of the bike arriving on time, but miraculously it did.
The bike itself is absolutely lovely. It arrived with a very minor scratch on the frame, but it's only noticeable if you scrutinise the bike ve y carefully.
Before purchasing the bike, I had some reservations about something so inexpensive, but I'm completely satisfied with my choice!
